attributionInfo.brokerName: Douglas Elliman Real Estate - The Sarkis Team

description: Telegraph Hill! Prime South Boston location steps to the newly restored Thomas Park. Sunny penthouse TRIFECTA with CENTRAL AIR, IN-UNIT LAUNDRY and PRIVATE DECK with amazing views! Initially converted to condominiums in 2004, this well-maintained 3-family, is fully owner occupied. Recent updates include new carpeting in hallways, repainted deck and front exterior of the building. Private storage unit and deeded roof rights for a future potential value-add. Wake up and have coffee on your private deck, take your dog to Castle Island, spend the day at M Street Beach and head over to Broadway for dinner. Conveniently located near Moakley Park, Carsen Beach, I-93, public transportation, Logan Airport, Downtown and Seaport. Seller welcomes offers with requests for buyer concessions.
